==English==

===Etymology===
First coined in 1382, from {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|zele|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|zel|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{term|zēlus|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|ζῆλος||zeal, jealousy|lang=grc}}, from {{term|ζηλόω||to emulate, to be jealous|lang=grc}}. Cognate to {{term|jealous|lang=en}}.

